Package: LDRegularization
Type: Package
Title: Regularization of Linkage Disequilibrium Matrix
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Yihe Yang
Maintainer: Yihe Yang <yxy1234@case.edu>
Description: This package provides methods for regularizing large-scale 
    linkage disequilibrium (LD) matrix. It implements a variety of 
    regularization techniques, including shrinkage, banding, tapering, 
    thresholding, and block thresholding, as well as their POET-based 
    extensions. The package enables efficient computation for high-dimensional 
    LD matrix, with selected functions implemented in C++ for performance 
    (via Rcpp and CppMatrix).
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends: 
    R (>= 2.10)
Imports:
    Rcpp,
    RcppArmadillo,
    CppMatrix
LinkingTo: 
    Rcpp,
    RcppArmadillo
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Config/testthat/edition: 3
